Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.21,0:00:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經很懦弱的 Yesterday
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想大哭一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.22,0:00:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以氣餒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.79,0:00:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論何時也不是孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.69,0:00:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙遠的夢想在閃耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.33,0:00:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將它找回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.70,0:00:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把雙眼閉上便可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.67,0:00:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在心中的一個角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.78,0:00:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算留下傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.10,0:00:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要害怕 現在是兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.34,0:01:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放棄 Step by Step
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.96,0:01:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓著夢想 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.50,0:01:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經常也和你一起向明天邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.97,0:01:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續前進 Step by Step
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想堅信著 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.81,0:01:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想向著天空大聲呼叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.12,0:01:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃燒著 in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.92,0:01:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫戰部渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.44,0:01:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了打倒支配了在遙遠天空上的星界山的多壞達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.45,0:01:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們以第七星界為目標展開了冒險旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.10,0:01:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在身處的是有趣熱帶的第四星界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.10,0:01:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追蹤著黑球來到複活島石像的城堡的我們面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.24,0:01:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了魔界三兄弟所乘的黑龍角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.04,0:01:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸被封進了暗黑空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.81,0:02:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也會是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.69,0:02:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二十八話\N超激鬥!龍星丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.69,0:02:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火子,餵,火子不要一直睡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.89,0:02:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起來,火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.50,0:02:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈…終於動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.57,0:02:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.11,0:02:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了,黑球呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.21,0:02:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,那個黑黑的球被那巨大的魔神拿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.59,0:02:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.88,0:02:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,失去了龍神丸的現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.04,0:02:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是個普通沒有力量的小鬼罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.86,0:02:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼,你已經不是什麼救世主了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被吸進了暗黑空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.72,0:02:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸便不會再回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你死心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.77,0:02:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.54,0:02:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星界山拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.80,0:02:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把星界山…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會放棄的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.62,0:03:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.36,0:03:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會放棄的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.21,0:03:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去把龍神丸帶回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.19,0:03:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.38,0:03:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會連你也不能回來的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真蠢材!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.31,0:03:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,節巴利、雪京芭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.01,0:03:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關閉暗黑空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.69,0:03:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把渡他們永遠封閉在黑暗之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以給你這樣做嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.71,0:03:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在渡回來之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會給你把出口關閉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.48,0:03:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這之前我們做你對手吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.02,0:03:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳,死不足惜的家夥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧,去死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.93,0:03:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們暫時便在這裏躺一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一會會好好了結你們的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即把暗黑空間關閉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.44,0:04:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.52,0:04:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.91,0:04:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生,把黑球還給我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.32,0:04:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油,火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混…混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.21,0:04:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏便是暗黑空間?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.98,0:04:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.16,0:04:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.89,0:04:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣去哪裏找才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.79,0:05:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救…救命!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.73,0:05:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好噁心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵,不要過來啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.11,0:05:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺負女孩子,不可饒恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.39,0:05:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真險呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.90,0:05:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最怕蜘蛛的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.49,0:05:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的,真是行衰運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.91,0:05:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,托你的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.36,0:05:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.37,0:05:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.20,0:05:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是暗黑空間的精靈艾瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是人類呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來這種地方幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來找一部叫龍神丸的魔神的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有沒有見過?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.07,0:05:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是剛才丟進來的魔神嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.18,0:05:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.01,0:05:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪裏見到的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.09,0:06:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,為了報答你救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶你去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.32,0:06:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.39,0:06:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要到龍神丸那裏的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.53,0:06:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過這個沼澤是捷徑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這裏不知道會有什麼東西襲擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.30,0:06:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有勇氣過去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.65,0:06:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.78,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像隱約有點不祥感覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.95,0:06:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?剛才不是還說有勇氣過去的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,雖然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.94,0:06:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?怎麼突然覺得很想睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.71,0:06:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以睡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡了會發生很可怕的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?可怕的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你這樣說也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.21,0:06:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明已叫他不可以睡的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.81,0:06:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.19,0:07:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我說過會發生很可怕的事了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷失了在這個世界的人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.09,0:07:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以讓他們有命回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.88,0:07:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何會這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會輸的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.72,0:07:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.64,0:08:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀…死了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.02,0:08:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為會死掉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.98,0:08:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呢,死了便好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.79,0:08:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.11,0:08:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.70,0:08:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾瑪小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.99,0:08:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,艾瑪小姐也沒事太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.78,0:08:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.31,0:08:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一點就過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.67,0:08:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這裏是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是死亡野原啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一踏進這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便只能看著前面走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.55,0:08:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.79,0:08:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一回頭的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體便會變成石頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變石頭!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.19,0:08:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣你也要去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.56,0:08:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了把龍神丸帶回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.90,0:08:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定會死的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.97,0:09:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅,你來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.15,0:09:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.14,0:09:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能回頭看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.22,0:09:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.58,0:09:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.84,0:09:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.20,0:09:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的劍和我的魚叉交換的約定怎樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.13,0:09:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡和我們玩賽跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.26,0:09:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.28,0:09:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏誰也沒有來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.27,0:09:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,等等啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.27,0:09:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.02,0:09:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.00,0:09:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.51,0:09:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.83,0:09:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.51,0:09:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好辛苦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快來救我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸他在求救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.32,0:09:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸,你在哪裏!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快救我,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.22,0:09:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好辛苦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.44,0:09:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體好像被火燒一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.96,0:10:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.30,0:10:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不來救我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.13,0:10:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.24,0:10:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.87,0:10:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.27,0:10:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所認識的龍神丸是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.24,0:10:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸是絕不會說示弱的話的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.44,0:10:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已穿過死亡野原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.16,0:10:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回頭看也沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.74,0:10:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才險些變成石頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.84,0:10:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.85,0:10:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.35,0:11:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等,龍神丸啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽不見我的聲音嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.60,0:11:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.93,0:11:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪裏!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.90,0:11:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸被黑暗石像奪去了意識了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.77,0:11:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗石像?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.07,0:11:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是支配著這個暗黑空間的可怕石像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.57,0:11:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.16,0:11:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這便是黑暗石像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進入了暗黑空間的魔神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.00,0:11:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都會被那石像握碎掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.64,0:11:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.55,0:11:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼龍神丸也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸,不可以去那邊的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.94,0:11:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了打倒那石像外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.79,0:11:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有其他方法救龍神丸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.44,0:11:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那石像?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.71,0:11:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要怎樣做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.28,0:11:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.54,0:12:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石像的額頭上有顆寶石吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它打破便可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.68,0:12:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.55,0:12:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去試試!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.58,0:12:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾瑪小姐在這裏等我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.75,0:12:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明做不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.87,0:12:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.43,0:12:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我不會輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真是看不下去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等我,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.53,0:12:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在來救你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.07,0:13:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾瑪小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.18,0:14:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石像變成了岩石了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.99,0:14:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的,今天真的是行大衰運呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.19,0:14:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾瑪小姐,你沒有事太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.02,0:14:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了,龍神丸呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.00,0:14:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧,艾瑪小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.54,0:14:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.56,0:14:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點,龍神丸…龍神丸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.81,0:14:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍…龍神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.08,0:14:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.38,0:14:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事?這把劍是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光龍劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.74,0:15:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有真正的救世主才能得到的光之劍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.27,0:15:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我會知道這些事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光龍劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.46,0:16:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你複活了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.43,0:16:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡重奪回來的這光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.20,0:16:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給了我力量呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.40,0:16:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多謝你,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.10,0:16:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不,不是我一個人的力量啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.10,0:16:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這裏的艾瑪小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾…艾瑪小姐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.33,0:16:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來黑暗石像便是為了封印光龍劍而建造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.39,0:16:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.61,0:16:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多壞達還把這光明空間變成了暗黑空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.93,0:16:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也被改變姿態失去了記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過,全靠渡的活躍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.48,0:16:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令這世界和我也恢複原狀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.14,0:16:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的真名叫芙麗亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是守護光龍劍的妖精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.81,0:16:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼,這把劍便應該要還給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.85,0:17:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.05,0:17:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把劍已經是你的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.92,0:17:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.91,0:17:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在外面封閉這空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.44,0:17:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,你趕快出發吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,那再見了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.17,0:17:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.59,0:17:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.09,0:17:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的力量已變得能把黑暗變為光明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.19,0:17:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那力量一定會令龍神丸得到新的力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.17,0:18:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍神丸,加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.04,0:18:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要輸給這樣的風!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.78,0:18:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.61,0:18:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,拔劍吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.45,0:18:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔劍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.53,0:18:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.59,0:18:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.83,0:18:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟被嘍囉們壞了我的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.20,0:18:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡…渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.35,0:18:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難…難道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.99,0:18:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.03,0:18:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.41,0:18:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的力量已變得能把黑暗變為光明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.36,0:18:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一種力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.89,0:19:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令我得到了新的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.47,0:19:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,你叫現在的我做龍星丸吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.75,0:19:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍星丸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.07,0:19:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.56,0:19:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍星丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.11,0:19:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡第一名,渡超了不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔界三兄弟!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.95,0:19:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次到救世主渡做你們對手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.36,0:19:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳,這樣的話再來多一次魔界力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送你去回不了來的地獄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.40,0:19:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.92,0:19:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.07,0:19:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會輸的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.03,0:19:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超炎龍拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.54,0:19:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.34,0:19:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是時候了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用光龍劍吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.98,0:19:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.44,0:20:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光龍劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.19,0:20:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個仇我一定會報的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.48,0:20:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我記著啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.09,0:20:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.60,0:20:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅、古拿瑪、火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.72,0:20:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下相信你一定會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.74,0:20:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且,龍神丸的力量也好像增強了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.14,0:20:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是會靠師傅和古拿瑪在牽制著黑龍角啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不向那家夥道謝也不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.62,0:20:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來那部魔神是海火子的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.12,0:21:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.12,0:21:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已沒有多壞達的手下在了呢
